### List all meters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/meters
Authorization: Bearer {{financeToken}}

### Register a new meter for a customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/meters
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meterNumber": "WTR-2026-9960",
  "meterType": "WATER",
  "installationDate": "2026-06-05",
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}"
}

### Get a meter by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/meters/{{meterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorToken}}

### List meters belonging to a customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/meters/customer/{{customerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorToken}}

### Activate / deactivate a meter
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/meters/{{meterId}}/status?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorToken}}